Mechanical circulatory support. An expert opinion of the Association of 
Intensive Cardiac Care and the Association of Cardiovascular Interventions of 
the Polish Cardiac Society.

Tycińska A(1), Grygier M(2), Biegus J(3), Czarnik T(4), Dąbrowski M(5), Depukat 
