National and subnational burden of disease attributable to occupational exposure 
to solar ultraviolet radiation (SUVR) in Iran, 2005-2019.

Saeedi R(1), Miri H(2), Abtahi M(3), Dobaradaran S(4), Koolivand A(5), Jorfi 
