Laminectomy and fusion in multilevel degenerative cervical myelopathy - 
Correlation between objective and subjective postoperative restriction of 
cervical spine mobility.

Scholz C(1), Masalha W(2), Naseri Y(3), Klingler JH(2), Hohenhaus M(2), Hubbe 
